    "Table 5 shows the analysis results with disclosure as the dependent variable.",
    "Model 1 examines the baseline impact of fixed effects on disclosure rates.",
    "Model 2 shows commercial potential strongly predicts disclosure, increasing explained variation beyond year-field fixed effects from 0.025 to 0.061."
